LUVCam: a package for LUVCam1 and 2 operations
==========================================

.. .. image:: https://zenodo.org/badge/DOI/10.5281/zenodo.1214268.svg
..    :target: https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1214268
..    :alt: DOI 10.5281/zenodo.1214268

